        <div class="section-text"><strong>Note:</strong> Hubstaff is not a keylogging program. It does not know what you are typing; rather, Hubstaff merely records whether your keyboard is active or inactive. All Well Pass Today screenshots are uploaded via SSL over the standard HTTPS
